  2. #3, #4 — Eliminate force-unwrap crash paths
  3. #7, #6 — Fix concurrency races (session token, operation state)
  4. #2 — Warn users about HTTP + token exposure
  5. #5, #9, #10 — Dead code / startup crash risk
  6. #11–#16 — Minor quality items
